PrecisReappointment of WILLIAM R. JAMES of Ottawa, Ontario, as Superintendent of Bankruptcy, on an interim basis, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of six months, or until a new Superintendent of Bankruptcy is appointed, whichever is earlier, effective September 30, 2012.
